    <h2>Eligibility</h2>
       <%= image_tag "eligibility.jpg", :alt=>"", :class=>"fright photo2" %>
    <p class="last">You are eligible to join One Vision Federal Credit Union if you <span class="bold">live, work, worship, or attend school in Clark, Floyd, or Harrison Counties in Indiana</span>. Your family is also eligible to join. See below for family eligibility. To join, you will need to fill out an application, pay a one-time membership fee of $1.00, and open a Prime Share Account with a minimum balance of $5.00. You can either fill out the membership application here online (you still need to make your initial deposit at a location) or stop by any of our two convenient locations at your convenience to speak to one of our Member Service Representatives. Once you become a member, you can then take advantage of our full array of financial products and services. Feel free to browse our website and find out all that One Vision Federal Credit Union has to offer you.</p>

    <h4>Family Eligibility</h4>
    <p>If you are eligible to join One Vision Federal Credit Union, then your family is also eligible to take advantage of the benefits we offer! Eligible family members include:</p>
