<p>All individuals permanently living in the primary member's household are also eligible for membership.</p>
<p>Once a member – you are always a member!</p>

<p class="bold underline">What you will need to become a member</p>
<ul>
<li>Valid and Current Driver's License</li>
<li>Proof of Address (if address on Driver's License is incorrect) such as a utility bill</li>
<li>$6.00 - $1 for membership fee and $5 to open your Prime Share account</li>
<li>Social Security Number</li>
</ul>

<p class="bold underline">What you will need when applying for a loan</p>
<ul>
<li>Must be a member</li>
<li>Two most recent paystubs</li>
<li>If loan is an auto loan, we will need a sales order for the vehicle, VIN number, and current auto insurance information</li>
<li>If loan is a first mortgage, we will need a copy of sales contract, last 2 years W-2's, last 30 days of paystubs, and last 3 months of checking
account statements</li>
<li>If loan is HELOC or 2nd Mortgage, we will need last 30 days of paystubs and proof of homeowners insurance</li>
</ul>
